      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has clearly been well-cared for by its previous owner. The exterior retains a strong shine, though you will find some minor stone chips on the front bumper and a few light surface scratches consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and free of any major stains or odors, with only minor wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car runs smoothly and has a consistent service history, making it a reliable choice for its next owner.",
