      "description": "We are proud to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained in absolute mint condition. This specimen features a flawless exterior finish and a pristine interior that reflects an extraordinary level of care and preservation. Mechanically superior and cosmetically unblemished, this motorcar represents a rare opportunity for the sophisticated buyer seeking a turn-key investment in automotive excellence.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
